        <title type="html"><![CDATA[河边]]></title>
        <id>https://testing-systems.github.io/post/he-bian/</id>
        <link href="https://testing-systems.github.io/post/he-bian/">
        </link>
        <updated>2025-05-04T10:24:27.000Z</updated>
        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>凉爽的风灌满我的宽大裤腿<br>
在路上甩甩手臂 身后有小电动车飞过</p>
<p>双臂怎么画圈也无法驶离地面<br>
噢，河边<br>
麻雀走在我前面</p>
<p>Riverwalk</p>
<p>Cool wind pours into my wide pants legs,<br>
my arms swing loosely as I walk.<br>
Scooters zip past like a thought.</p>
<p>No matter how I spin,<br>
the ground pulls me in.</p>
<p>Sparrows walk ahead of me<br>
on the railing, then take flight—<br>
certain of the way.</p>
